description:
A THUNDEROUS, FURY-FILLED TALE .

My name is Arawn. I am the lord of scorched earth. I thought I knew my enemy. I thought it far from me, in the land of Erin ... I was wrong. It had always been there. Closer. Close to my heart. I thought it my ally, my friend, my companion. I had blind faith in him. I listened to his words, the cauldron of blood ... but he used me as he used another. to fulfill his evil plan ...

.
